OL,3,CBaby girl died after 'selfish' parents
OL,4,Cwent off-grid, court told
OL,6,FA baby girl died after her "cruel and
OL,7,Farrogant" parents went on the run and
OL,8,Flived "off grid" in a tent, a court
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FAfter the baby died, Constance Marten,
OL,12,F36, and Mark Gordon, 49, left her in a
OL,13,Fdisused shed inside a shopping bag
OL,14,Fcovered in rubbish "as if she was
OL,15,Frefuse", the Old Bailey was told.
OL,17,FJurors heard that the infant was the
OL,18,Fcouple's fifth baby, their other
OL,19,Fchildren having previously been taken
OL,20,Finto care.
