OL,3,CBaby girl died after 'selfish' parents
OL,4,Cwent off-grid, court told
OL,6,FIt was their "selfish desire" to keep
OL,7,Fthe baby that ultimately led to her
OL,8,F"entirely avoidable" death, prosecutor
OL,9,FTom Little KC said on Thursday.
OL,11,FOpening their trial, Mr Little said
OL,12,Fthe baby "would still be alive if it
OL,13,Fwas not for the reckless, utterly
OL,14,Fselfish, callous, cruel, arrogant and
OL,15,Fultimately grossly negligent conduct
OL,16,Fof the two defendants on trial".
OL,18,FHe told jurors: "They put their
OL,19,Frelationship and their view of life
OL,20,Fbefore the life of a little baby girl."
