OL,3,CBaby girl died after 'selfish' parents
OL,4,Cwent off-grid, court told
OL,6,FMr Little said the defendants decided
OL,7,Fthey "knew best" and ignored the
OL,8,Fadvice they were given rather than act
OL,9,Fin the vulnerable baby's best
OL,10,Finterests.
OL,12,F"They decided that, in the middle of a
OL,13,Fcold winter and in cruel and obviously
OL,14,Fdangerous weather conditions, they
OL,15,Fwould deprive the baby of what it
OL,16,Fneeded ` warmth, shelter and food and
OL,17,Fultimately safety," he said.
