OL,3,CBaby girl died after 'selfish' parents
OL,4,Cwent off-grid, court told
OL,6,F"They essentially went off-grid and
OL,7,Flived in a tent with hardly any
OL,8,Fclothes, no means of keeping and
OL,9,Fremaining warm and dry, and with
OL,10,Fscarcely any food.
OL,12,F"Their selfish desire to keep their
OL,13,Fbaby girl led inexorably to the death
OL,14,Fof that very baby.
OL,16,F"They went, and remained, on the run.
OL,17,FGiving birth to the baby on the run.
OL,18,FNot seeking any medical assistance
OL,19,Fbefore, during or after birth. Not
OL,20,Fregistering the birth but moving from
OL,21,Flocation to location.
