OL,3,CBaby girl died after 'selfish' parents
OL,4,Cwent off-grid, court told
OL,6,F"When the hunt by the authorities to
OL,7,Ffind them, which became national front
OL,8,Fpage news almost exactly a year ago,
OL,9,Fintensified, so their desperate
OL,10,Fselfishness increased and so did the
OL,11,Frisks and the dangers to the baby."
OL,13,FThe couple began camping in "freezing
OL,14,Fand obviously dangerous conditions" on
OL,15,Fthe South Downs with insufficient
OL,16,Fclothes, equipment and food and no
OL,17,Fmedical assistance, the court was told.
