OL,3,CBaby girl died after 'selfish' parents
OL,4,Cwent off-grid, court told
OL,6,FMr Little said: "That baby never stood
OL,7,Fa chance. After the baby had died, the
OL,8,Fdefendants did not hand themselves in
OL,9,Fbut instead remained off-grid and
OL,10,Ftrying to hide, leaving the body of
OL,11,Ftheir dead baby in a shopping bag
OL,12,Fcovered in rubbish, as if she was
OL,13,Frefuse, and left in a disused unlocked
OL,14,Fshed."
OL,16,FThe couple, of no fixed address, deny
OL,17,Fmanslaughter by gross negligence of
OL,18,Fthe girl between January 4 and
OL,19,FFebruary 27 last year.
